title: #92Noon! Gleeman/Grimm/Thiry/Birk/Presser
description: Why on Earth is Panthers TE Greg Olsen being allowed in the broadcast booth for Vikings/Rams this weekend? Gleeman in studio, Gophers VOX Mike Grimm joins, LA Times scribe Lindsey Thiry helps with Vikes/Rams preview & LA traffic, the weekly Birk Bit, and a replay of Zimmer's presser!
